Question: The right image shows one panda posed on its back with at least one front paw raised and mouth open.

Reference Answer: True

Left image URL: http://www.sichuanfun.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/panda-facts-4.jpg

Original program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is the panda posed on its back?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is at least one front paw raised?')
ANSWER2=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is the mouth open?')
ANSWER3=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} and {ANSWER1} and {ANSWER2}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER3)
```
